<plot>Helen, a young woman recently moved in with her fiancé, Gabriel. They live on a farm and share a common passion, raising horses. They met at a well-known bar in Montreal. It was love at first sight and they moved in together not long after. One day she begins to have visions that frighten her. That same night she invites her friends for a supper to celebrate her engagement but Gabriel does not show up.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?598585</url></doc>
